<p id="_cda1789e-5278-0fb9-7d5a-fffdc995b797">Let us now look at the development of a Bernoullian sum <stem type="MathML" block="false"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <msub>
      <mtext/>
      <mi>r</mi>
    </msub>
    <msub>
      <mstyle mathvariant="italic">
        <mi>S</mi>
      </mstyle>
