<asciimath>""_r ii(S)_n = ... + 1/r ((r),(r-1)) ii(B)_r t^(r+1-r) = ... + ii(B)_rt.</asciimath></stem></formula>

<p id="_acd29f24-52b2-03f9-fa74-6f2e8ba6be13">We note in passing that <stem type="MathML" block="false"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <msub>
