</math>
<asciimath>""_rZZ_n</asciimath></stem>.</p>

<p id="_3265aa69-d38f-9d70-4b13-0e81ca144272">The two cases with <stem type="MathML" block="false"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
